**** Purpose: Mostrar comandos COBOL (ACCEPT)

IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. DATAHORA.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
77 WS-MOSTRA            PIC X(20) VALUE SPACES.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.

     ACCEPT WS-MOSTRA FROM DATE           * Data formato americano
     DISPLAY WS-MOSTRA
    
     ACCEPT WS-MOSTRA FROM DATE YYYYMMDD * Data mostrando ano com 4 dígitos
     DISPLAY WS-MOSTRA
     
     ACCEPT WS-MOSTRA FROM DAY           * Ano e numero do dia do ano 
     DISPLAY WS-MOSTRA
     
     ACCEPT WS-MOSTRA FROM DAY YYYYDDD   * Ano com 4 digitos e dia do ano
     DISPLAY WS-MOSTRA
     
     ACCEPT WS-MOSTRA FROM DAY-OF-WEEK   * Dia da semana, neste caso Thursday
     DISPLAY WS-MOSTRA
     
     ACCEPT WS-MOSTRA FROM TIME          * Hora, minuto, segundo, milésimo de segundo
     DISPLAY WS-MOSTRA
STOP RUN.


